title: North American International Auto Racing Show, Detroit - /SHAKEDOWN
description: NAIAS, the Detroit Auto Show, is this week.  Instead of covering cars that mean nothing to motorsport, Leo Parente starts a list of race cars we'd want on the show floor.  Now, you need to finish the list, adding your brands / racecars that should be on display.
